messages.text: The strappy red dress. I want him to see what he’ll be missing.
Ok. Article drops in a half hour. Going to make it on time?
Should just be sitting down to dinner.
Are you running the picture I sent you?
The one of him and that woman jewelry shopping? Yeah. Where did you get it anyway?
Because you forwarded the e-mail from GoldenGrahams@Yahoo.com.
Vera? You’re not back with Graham, are you?
No, it’s not. He’s the jerk who hired this guy, remember?
Because he knew I’d take the assignment.
I just don’t want to see you get tricked.
Don’t you see. It’s still the game.
You fell for Topher then you realized he’s a bad guy. Now Graham doesn’t look so bad.
I’ll be fine. I’m not the one who’s about to get burned.
Look. I promise I won’t bother you again after tonight.
Hey buddy. Got big plans tonight?
You finally got it right. I’m proud of you, Graham.
As a matter of fact, your EX-fiance and I are going to dinner.
So this is the date where someone gets dumped, right?
Nothing. Just wouldn't want you to profess your love or anything only to get…
I appreciate the concern but I think i’ll be just fine.
Article goes live in ten minutes.
He’s pacing back and forth outside.
Think he knows about the article?
He’s tucking it in his pocket.
Maybe it’s part of the game.
I don’t know. He doesn’t look like his usual self.
Maybe he feels bad this time.
Like he actually cares about me?
You’re the one who kept saying it was all a game!!!
I don’t know! He just doesn’t seem like the type to get nervous.
What if I told you that after tonight, not only will someone get burned, but someone else will get the girl.
Told you I’m not going to burn her.
And I told you it’s not her I’m worried about.
So what? I get burned and you get the girl?
Must be nice  to live in your little fantasyland.
He keeps reaching into his coat pocket.
We’re going live in less than five.
You still want to go through with it, right?
Is that seriously on the table?
What if he really likes me?
I don’t know what to do.
He just excused himself to the bathroom.
All right, enough with the games. What’s going on?
Sucks not being in control, huh?
Graham, what do you know that you’re not telling?
You said you’d refund me the money.
If you want to know the truth, transfer the cash.
I don’t have much time left if you want to stop this.
Do you want to stop it?
Is he still in the bathroom?
This is a limited time offer, Topher.
It takes a minute to transfer this kind of money.
A minute is all you have.
You know the picture we’re running of him in the jewelry shop with that other woman…
They were looking at a necklace.
He wasn't dating her. She was helping him pick it out!
Wish you’d figured that out a few seconds ago.
He just ran out of the restaurant.
He was going to give me this necklace. He was never going to burn me…
Well, what are you waiting for?
Who was the girl in the picture???
I don’t know. What’s it matter?
He wasn’t running the game on her, was he?
If you want another shot with me, you have to be honest.
Vera, it could have been another woman.
You’re really going to choose him over me? He’s a conman!
No, I’m the one who loves you.
And I’m the one who doesn’t love you back.
Think you said it all pretty well in that article.
Just some words that express what you think of me.
I thought it was still a game!
I did all those terrible things.
But I see another side of you. A better side.
I know. That’s why I fell for you.
What were you going to do with the necklace?
We see if there’s a spark.
